The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Cool kitchens

 TITHI SARKAR

 Model Sheena at the launch of a Kitchen Grace store on Wednesday. Picture by Rashbehari Das 

 What: Launch of IDesigns Kitchen Grace store.

 Where: 1-C, Ashutosh Mukherjee Road, near Elgin Road crossing.

 When: Wednesday.

 Take a look: IDesigns new store designs your kitchen in a convenient, effective and affordable way. Model Sheena displayed the collection of modular kitchens at the store. 

 The modular cabinets come in particle board, marine ply, aluminium frame, steel and wood, with a host of inner space arrangement and door designs. 

 Other kitchen appliances like chimney hoods, hobs, sinks and midway accessories are also available here. 

 Depending on the space, requirement, lifestyle, decor and budget of the client, IDesign helps choose the right material, colour and design, and to set it up.

 Pocket pinch: Prices range between Rs 3,000 and Rs 80,000.

 Voiceover: We do not dump products on our clients; we design kitchens. Someone may want to do up a part of his/her kitchen now and renovate the rest after a year or two. We will be able to provide the same material and finish even then, said Kiran Rajan, owner of the store.




